EnableRedistribution_MerkleVCA_Integration_Test
├── when caller not campaign creator
│  └── it should revert
└── when caller campaign creator
   ├── given vesting end time not in future
   │  └── it should revert
   └── given vesting end time in future
      ├── given redistribution enabled
      │  └── it should revert
      └── given redistribution not enabled
         ├── it should enable redistribution
         └── it should emit {RedistributionEnabled} event
